# Willy IoT Netlist
BOARD arduino uno
NETS 9

N001 UNO 5V -> U1 VCC [PWR_5V]
N002 UNO GND -> U1 GND [GND]
N003 UNO D2 -> U1 CLK [CLK]
N004 UNO D3 -> U1 DIO [DIO]
N005 UNO 5V -> S1 VCC [PWR_5V]
N006 UNO GND -> S1 GND [GND]
N007 UNO D4 -> S1 DATA [DATA]
N008 UNO D4 -> R1 10k pull-up [PULLUP]
N009 R1 other end -> UNO 5V [PULLUP_5V]
